    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Draftsmen who do rendering, especially those who produce drawings of architectural designs in accurate, representational perspective to show what the project will look like when built.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
